    <data key="d0">ContactSuite Contact Center Scale Architecture</data>
    <data key="d1">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=BPvr0qWpJlA</data>
    <data key="d2">Integrates AWS Connect, SES, and local custom microservices to empower support agents with smart screen pops and automated CRM data retrieval.</data>
